{"tid":1642973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧穎芝為良知失長期飯票","createTime":"2019-10-10T02:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T13:44:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f97f71c49c472535bb1dde417164262b0814fd1","tid":1642973,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191010/20783972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191010%2F20783972&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX52LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=5a04e7d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191010%2F20783972&h=8ab72d46\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20191010/20783972</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧穎芝為良知失長期飯票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191010/large/1570629943_e259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191010%2Flarge%2F1570629943_e259.jpg&h=312633e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧穎芝昨日在Ig貼文，指自己因為良知失去長期飯票，更揚言「解約就解約吧」。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n鄧穎芝（Vangie）近年不時到內地登台，收入不錯，但昨日凌晨她突然在Ig story出post留言：「因為良知，失去了長期飯票。我有手有腳，唔上去唱都唔會餓死的，香港人，加油！解約就解約吧！」背景疑似是一張Vangie在內地登台的相片。其後她再出post，貼出一張課金「立場新聞」email的收據相片，再留言問大家：「你課咗未？」疑似政治表態。<br />\n<br />\n昨日《蘋果》向Vangie了解，她以短訊回覆：「其實暫時冇乜嘢可以回應，要講嘅已經表達咗，良知同錢，我揀良知，自己只想盡力做個有良心嘅香港人，其他不回應了，都唔想放大呢件事，想低調做回香港人，謝謝。希望你諒解。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：皓騫 <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：每件售價逾3千元<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n阮民安斥香港冇法治<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\nTiffany撤遮眼廣告<br />\n<br />\n每件售價逾3千元<br />\n楊明店舖變黃：員工自行貼上<br />\n阮民安斥香港冇法治<br />\nTiffany撤遮眼廣告<br />\n着自家潮店&times;姚明11號做生招牌陳冠希火箭隊球衣 被指辱華要求下架"},{"pid":"839ded7727786da7e5fa6b7f71d78c49c18f5877","tid":1642973,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:46:24.000Z","msg":"[反共聯合陣線][品蔥建議] 現時的當務之急是建立一個內地反賊與香港抗爭人士的溝通渠道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642985\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642985</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34ef1da3eddab5c7fbb2a89f80baa3660b64fd1e","tid":1642973,"uid":211461,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"多謝發聲 但都想問句who"},{"pid":"1d3f713a95738d9a3407b54b1cbb0e91a18fb9f4","tid":1642973,"uid":104804,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34ef1da3eddab5c7fbb2a89f80baa3660b64fd1e","tid":1642973,"uid":211461,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"多謝發聲 但都想問句who"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"聽下苦情人啦屌你"},{"pid":"343f7bb396abf727f698ab26c3b75bedfd89f4e3","tid":1642973,"uid":196803,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"佢首苦情人好好聽"},{"pid":"f7addf341fb6460625db1601507b264357695963","tid":1642973,"uid":299372,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"之前佢先屌完我地既 TL bb喎？<br />\n又串人基佬反鄉黑做show又盛，果時好多連登仔屌佢得首苦情人，仲低成就過TL<br />\n而家又上神臺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388722551093f9169244054df811a4221155362a","tid":1642973,"uid":179348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"343f7bb396abf727f698ab26c3b75bedfd89f4e3","tid":1642973,"uid":196803,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"佢首苦情人好好聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T03:54:52.000Z","msg":"得一首歌講到失長期飯票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181b530723b5baee5cdfb5822db5e4ee1768f21b","tid":1642973,"uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"仗義每多屠狗輩"},{"pid":"33bca214a92e48857dbe74207c4b2c1399e8f9d9","tid":1642973,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":